<h1>4. User Testing & Marketing Collateral</h1>

<h2>4.1 User Testing & Validation Report</h2>
<p><b>Target Respondents:</b> 10 University IT students and 2 General Services staff members.</p>
<p><b>Testing Method:</b> Usability testing via Vercel live link deployment, followed by a short Google Form survey.</p>
<p><b>Results and Feedback:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><b>Ease of Use:</b> 100% of student respondents found the "New Request" form extremely intuitive, praising the clear priority dropdown.</li>
<li><b>Admin Satisfaction:</b> Staff members appreciated the dynamic pie chart, noting it instantly showed them which areas needed the most attention.</li>
<li><b>Speed:</b> Users reported that submitting a ticket took an average of only 12 seconds compared to the 5-minute process of filling out paper forms at the maintenance office.</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Improvements Made based on Feedback:</b></p>
<ul>
<li><i>Initial Feedback:</i> Users didn't know if their ticket was successfully submitted.</li>
<li><i>Improvement Implemented:</i> We added a "Toast Notification" popup that confirms "Ticket Submitted Successfully!" in the bottom right corner of the screen.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4.2 Social Media Pubmat Copy (For Facebook/University Groups)</h2>
<p><b>Headline:</b> Tired of waiting for broken campus facilities to get fixed? 🛠️</p>
<p><b>Body:</b></p>
<p>Introducing the <b>Maintenance & Monitoring System (MMS)</b>! We are bringing Baliuag University’s facility management into the digital age. No more lost paper forms. No more waiting in line at the General Services office.</p>
<p>With MMS, you can:</p>
<ul>
<li>✅ Report broken lights, aircons, or leaks in under 10 seconds.</li>
<li>✅ Track your request's real-time status.</li>
<li>✅ Access the portal instantly from your phone browser—no app download required!</li>
</ul>
<p><b>Call to Action:</b> Ready to experience a smarter campus? Try our live prototype today at: <b>https://mms-prototype-liart.vercel.app</b></p>

